    "glp1_listicle": {
      "type": "bloomli-glp1-listicle",
      "blocks": {
        "r1": {
          "type": "reason",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Why hair sheds during rapid weight loss",
            "caption": "Close-up of a hairbrush by a sunlit bathroom sink — calm, not clinical",
            "body": "<p>Rapid weight loss can nudge more of your hair into its natural resting-and-shedding phase, and eating less often means fewer of the nutrients hair relies on are coming in. It is common, and for most women it is temporary.*</p>"
          }
        },
        "r2": {
          "type": "reason",
          "settings": {
            "title": "It fills the nutrient gaps that matter for hair",
            "caption": "Flat-lay of the gummy bottle with passion fruit and B-vitamin-rich foods",
            "body": "<p>Smaller meals can mean less biotin, zinc, B-vitamins and protein reaching your hair. Bloomli delivers 6,000mcg biotin, marine collagen, zinc and a full B-complex to help fill the gaps that matter most.*</p>"
          }
        },
        "r3": {
          "type": "reason",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Biotin, done right",
            "caption": "Two passion-fruit gummies resting in an open palm on a cream surface",
            "body": "<p>Biotin on its own is only part of the story. Bloomli pairs 6,000mcg biotin with PABA and a full B-complex, so it works as part of a fuller routine rather than a single nutrient doing all the lifting.*</p>"
          }
        },
        "r4": {
          "type": "reason",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Two gummies, nothing to choke down",
            "caption": "Woman 35–45 smiling, taking her morning gummies in a bright kitchen",
            "body": "<p>Appetite and nausea can already be a lot on a GLP-1. Bloomli is two passion-fruit gummies a day, not another large capsule to get down.</p>"
          }
        },
        "r5": {
          "type": "reason",
          "settings": {
            "title": "A simple daily ritual that fits your new routine",
            "caption": "Bottle on a bathroom shelf beside a glass of water — a daily ritual",
            "body": "<p>Hair responds to consistency more than intensity. Two gummies a day is the kind of small habit that is easy to keep while so much else about your routine is changing.</p>"
          }
        },
        "r6": {
          "type": "reason",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Built for the long game",
            "caption": "Woman running fingers through healthy, down hair in soft natural light",
            "body": "<p>Hair grows in cycles, so this is a slow build. Roughly 4 to 12 weeks to support the look of less shedding, and 3 to 6 months for fuller-looking hair.* No overnight promises. The women who notice the most are the ones who stay consistent.</p>"
          }
        },
        "r7": {
          "type": "reason",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Tested, transparent, made in the USA",
            "caption": "The bottle on a clean cream surface with a folded COA document beside it",
            "body": "<p>COA and lot-testing documents on file. Made in the USA in an NSF/GMP-registered facility. Simple, traceable, and made to a standard you can ask us about.</p>"
          }
        },
        "provider": {
          "type": "callout",
          "settings": {
            "show_icon": true,
            "heading": "Keep your provider in the loop.",
            "body": "<p>Shedding during rapid weight loss is common and usually temporary. If you are concerned about any side effect you are experiencing on your medication, talk to your healthcare provider. Bloomli is a daily nutritional supplement, not a substitute for medical advice.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
